- At 150 feet. Aye, sir.
- 1 MC.

01:26:01.390 --> 01:26:02.682
Aye, sir.

01:26:03.892 --> 01:26:06.227
<i>May I have your attention, please.</i>

01:26:06.269 --> 01:26:12.233
<i>Crew of the USS Alabama,
attempted mutiny has been put down.</i>

01:26:13.694 --> 01:26:15.778
<i>We'll maintain security alert.</i>

01:26:15.862 --> 01:26:18.698
<i>Authorised movement
only in two-man teams.</i>

01:26:19.533 --> 01:26:21.826
<i>In the absence
of further radio communication,</i>

01:26:21.910 --> 01:26:24.537
<i>on orders from
the National Command Centre,</i>

01:26:24.579 --> 01:26:27.123
