01:26:57.988 --> 01:27:01.949
<i>This is the captain.
Mr Zimmer is the new X.O.</i>

01:27:04.369 --> 01:27:06.787
<i>Set condition 1 SQ.</i>

01:27:10.459 --> 01:27:13.878
<i>Spin up missiles one through five
and 20 through 24</i>

01:27:13.962 --> 01:27:15.588
<i>for strategic launch.</i>

01:27:15.630 --> 01:27:18.549
<i>The use of nuclear weapons
has been authorised.</i>

01:27:18.633 --> 01:27:20.259
<i>This is the X.O.</i>

01:27:21.511 --> 01:27:28.476
Weapons, Conn,
confirm target package SLBM 64741/2

01:27:28.518 --> 01:27:31.353
<i>for missiles one through five
and 20 through 24.</i>

01:27:31.438 --> 01:27:34.523
<i>- Target package confirmation, sir.
- This is the captain.</i>

01:27:43.992 --> 01:27:49.830
Conn, Weapons,
confirm target package SLBM 64741/2

01:27:49.915 --> 01:27:52.625
for missiles one through five
and 20 through 24.

01:27:52.667 --> 01:27:54.251
Aye, sir.

01:28:03.553 --> 01:28:06.430
Look, it's not a mutiny.
I did everything by the book.

01:28:06.515 --> 01:28:08.724
It's not about the book.

01:28:08.809 --> 01:28:12.353
If the Russians are gonna launch
and we do nothing,

01:28:12.437 --> 01:28:13.979
who's gonna stop 'em?

01:28:14.022 --> 01:28:16.649
Half of me is glad
the captain came back.

01:28:16.691 --> 01:28:18.692
He could be right, you know.

01:28:18.735 --> 01:28:21.362
No orders are valid, Cob,
if they're wrong.

01:28:21.446 --> 01:28:24.573
- We don't know if they're wrong.
- That's true. We don't know.

01:28:24.658 --> 01:28:26.867
That's why we have to find out first.

01:28:34.543 --> 01:28:37.127
What if Radchenko surrendered
and it's over?

01:28:38.255 --> 01:28:41.340
We launch. They see us. They launch.

01:28:43.510 --> 01:28:46.595
Our birds pass each other in the air.
Boom!

01:28:46.680 --> 01:28:49.056
- What do you got?
- Nuclear war.

01:28:49.307 --> 01:28:51.016
Nuclear holocaust.

01:28:57.899 --> 01:29:00.526
- What are you doing down here?
- Jesus, I was just going to the bath...

01:29:00.569 --> 01:29:02.695
Rivetti, nobody moves alone!
Come on. You know the drill.

01:29:02.737 --> 01:29:04.905
What, Bennefield,
I need an escort to take a shit?

01:29:04.990 --> 01:29:06.407
Shut up!

01:29:07.075 --> 01:29:09.243
Now I'm gonna call Control.
You stay right there.

01:29:09.327 --> 01:29:11.453
- Fuck that.
- I mean it, man.

01:29:16.918 --> 01:29:19.420
Okay, Moebius, open the door.

01:29:19.504 --> 01:29:22.172
- You broke my nose, man.
