01:29:25.719 --> 01:29:28.429
- Mr Rivetti, I'm impressed.
- I never liked him, sir.

01:29:28.471 --> 01:29:31.432
Rivetti, go to laundry. Get four sets
of coveralls and four caps.

01:29:31.516 --> 01:29:34.268
- Aye, sir.
- Just relax.

01:29:39.566 --> 01:29:41.942
Can I talk to you a second?

01:29:42.944 --> 01:29:44.194
Come on.

01:29:46.656 --> 01:29:48.282
- Everybody ready?
- Let's do it.

01:29:58.835 --> 01:30:02.421
- We're with you, sir.
- Let's go.

01:30:11.681 --> 01:30:14.725
- Approaching launch depth.
- Very well.

01:30:15.477 --> 01:30:17.645
Make your depth 150 feet.

01:30:18.647 --> 01:30:20.356
Zero bubble. Commence hovering.

01:30:20.440 --> 01:30:22.358
Zero bubble.
Commence hovering. Aye, sir.

01:30:22.442 --> 01:30:25.653
Conn, Weapons, estimated time
to weapons system 1 SQ

01:30:25.695 --> 01:30:27.821
three minutes, 30 seconds, sir.

01:30:28.949 --> 01:30:32.660
Conn, Weapons, Russian missiles
will have launch capability

01:30:32.702 --> 01:30:33.786
<i>in 12 minutes.</i>

01:30:33.828 --> 01:30:35.120
<i>Opening missile hatches.</i>

01:30:52.931 --> 01:30:56.225
<i>- Weps.
- Weps, this is Hunter. Listen to me.</i>

01:30:57.560 --> 01:30:59.770
- Where are you?
- Don't worry about where I am.

01:30:59.938 --> 01:31:00.980
You cannot proceed.

01:31:01.022 --> 01:31:02.564
We got other ships out there
that can handle this.

01:31:02.649 --> 01:31:04.692
You can't be influenced by the captain
or anybody else.

01:31:04.776 --> 01:31:06.110
Make up your own mind.

01:31:07.195 --> 01:31:09.697
Conn, Weapons,
estimated time to missile launch,

01:31:09.781 --> 01:31:11.532
<i>three minutes and counting, sir.</i>

01:31:11.616 --> 01:31:13.784
Weps, Weps, listen. Don't do this.

01:31:13.868 --> 01:31:15.619
<i>Don't do this. Once you launch,
they cannot come back.</i>

01:31:15.704 --> 01:31:16.870
<i>They cannot come back, Weps.</i>

01:31:16.913 --> 01:31:19.081
<i>And you know the repercussions
if we're wrong, goddamn it!</i>

01:31:19.165 --> 01:31:23.377
Weps, if we fire now, we'll be firing
while we're blind and crippled.

01:31:23.420 --> 01:31:24.503
You understand me?

01:31:24.546 --> 01:31:27.881
<i>- Where the fuck are you?
- Do not remove that firing trigger!</i>

01:31:27.924 --> 01:31:29.883
<i>Do not open the safe, Weps!
It's up to you!</i>

01:31:29.926 --> 01:31:33.637
You're the only one that knows
the combination! It's up to you, Weps!

01:31:33.722 --> 01:31:35.264
It's up to you.

01:31:38.351 --> 01:31:40.352
Mind your fuckin' panel!

01:31:47.193 --> 01:31:49.611
- You guys ready?
- Just about, sir.

01:31:53.366 --> 01:31:55.242
Radio, X.O. Vossler?

01:31:55.285 --> 01:31:57.286
X.O, Radio.

01:31:57.370 --> 01:32:00.539
- Sir, I don't know, sir.
- Vossler, calm down. Just calm down.

01:32:00.582 --> 01:32:03.876
<i>- Take a deep breath. Are you calm?
- Yeah, sort of.</i>

01:32:03.918 --> 01:32:05.169
Get the radio fixed, Vossler.

01:32:05.253 --> 01:32:07.588
I could have built one by now.
How long is it gonna take you?

01:32:07.672 --> 01:32:09.131
I don't know.

01:32:10.675 --> 01:32:13.052
Well, how much time do you need?

01:32:15.138 --> 01:32:16.263
Shit!

01:32:16.681 --> 01:32:17.931
Let's go.

01:32:21.853 --> 01:32:27.066
Missile tubes one through five
and 20 through 24 at 1 SQ, sir.

01:32:31.196 --> 01:32:35.574
Ship is hovering on automatic.
Dive is at 1 SQ, Captain.

01:32:36.951 --> 01:32:39.578
Missiles at 1 SQ. Ready to launch, sir.

01:32:46.377 --> 01:32:48.712
Sir, weapons system is at 1 SQ.

01:32:49.631 --> 01:32:52.758
- Missiles are ready for launch, sir.
- Very well.

01:32:53.760 --> 01:32:55.469
- Weapons.
- Aye, sir.

01:32:56.679 --> 01:32:59.598
Weapons, Conn,
remove the tactical firing trigger.

01:33:11.903 --> 01:33:13.862
- 1 MC.
- Aye, sir.

01:33:15.156 --> 01:33:18.659
Weapons, this is the captain.
Unlock the tactical firing trigger.

01:33:23.498 --> 01:33:24.623
Weps?

01:33:26.417 --> 01:33:28.836
Missiles are ready to launch, man.

01:33:31.840 --> 01:33:32.965
Sir.

01:33:36.636 --> 01:33:37.761
Shit.

01:33:38.638 --> 01:33:42.683
Mr Zimmer, no one is to touch this key.

01:33:43.059 --> 01:33:45.269
I'm going to launch
from missile control.

01:33:45.353 --> 01:33:47.604
- Aye, aye, sir.
- Westergaurd.

01:33:47.689 --> 01:33:49.606
- Sir.
- Dougherty. Come with me.

01:33:49.732 --> 01:33:53.277
- Mr Mahoney, take the conn.
- Aye, sir. I have the conn.

01:33:55.363 --> 01:33:58.365
What are you doing, man?
We're at 1 SQ. We're ready.

01:34:01.077 --> 01:34:02.661
<i>- Mr Dougherty.
- Aye.</i>

01:34:02.704 --> 01:34:05.831
- Station your guards fore and aft.
- Last two, forward hatch!

01:34:05.874 --> 01:34:07.708
First two, aft hatch!

01:34:09.460 --> 01:34:11.545
They're gonna fire from missile control.

01:34:12.922 --> 01:34:15.174
We've got to get back to the conn
and disarm the system. Come on.

01:34:15.216 --> 01:34:17.634
We'll travel in the crawl spaces.

01:34:32.734 --> 01:34:34.067
Mr Ince!

01:34:36.237 --> 01:34:39.072
Mr Ince, remove the tactical firing key.

01:34:39.949 --> 01:34:41.867
Sir, it is my duty to...

01:34:41.910 --> 01:34:45.412
Son, don't talk to me about duty.
Open the fucking safe!

01:34:56.257 --> 01:34:57.549
I can't do that, sir.

01:35:05.433 --> 01:35:07.267
I'm gonna count to three,

01:35:07.310 --> 01:35:08.769
and then I'm gonna blow
your fucking head off.

01:35:08.853 --> 01:35:09.978
One.

01:35:12.815 --> 01:35:13.941
<i>Two.</i>

01:35:18.196 --> 01:35:19.321
Shit!

01:35:21.699 --> 01:35:23.158
It does me no good to kill you.

01:35:23.243 --> 01:35:26.286
You're the only one
that knows the combination.

01:35:28.665 --> 01:35:30.207
However...

01:35:30.959 --> 01:35:35.462
Petty Officer Hilaire
doesn't know the combination!

01:35:37.590 --> 01:35:42.177
Millions of lives at stake here, Peter!
Don't make a dumb decision! One!

01:35:43.972 --> 01:35:47.474
- Two!
- Sir!

01:36:12.500 --> 01:36:13.875
<i>- Cob!
- Yo.</i>

01:36:13.960 --> 01:36:16.253
You and Hunsicker are going
to enter the conn from the bow.

01:36:16.337 --> 01:36:18.505
Rivetti, Linkletter and myself
will come in through the aft.

01:36:18.548 --> 01:36:20.215
You jump right on Zimmer, okay?

01:36:38.151 --> 01:36:39.818
Come on, come on!

01:36:44.324 --> 01:36:45.699
- Fire control ready?
- Aye, sir.

01:36:45.742 --> 01:36:47.409
- Launcher ready?
- Aye, sir.

01:36:48.494 --> 01:36:49.661
Initiate fire.

01:36:49.704 --> 01:36:51.621
- Freeze! Hold it, sir!
- Drop the weapon now!

01:36:51.706 --> 01:36:54.833
Move forward! Move forward!
Move, move, move! Get his pistol!

01:36:55.376 --> 01:36:59.296
- Fire one!
- Number one did not fire, sir.

01:37:01.341 --> 01:37:03.884
Sir, the captain's key
has been removed.

01:37:04.969 --> 01:37:06.178
Hunter.

01:37:07.638 --> 01:37:09.848
- You're a piece of shit.
- Son of a bitch.

01:37:10.600 --> 01:37:12.392
All right, you and you,
man the forward hatches.

01:37:12.477 --> 01:37:14.436
- Aye, sir.
- You, man the aft hatches.

01:37:14.520 --> 01:37:16.563
- Aye, sir.
- We're going up to periscope depth.

01:37:16.647 --> 01:37:18.857
We're gonna
reestablish communications

01:37:18.900 --> 01:37:21.985
and get that radio message.
Now anybody got a problem with that?

01:37:23.738 --> 01:37:25.322
Chief of the Boat,
make your depth 78 feet.

01:37:25.406 --> 01:37:27.032
Aye-aye, sir. Make your depth 78 feet.

01:37:27.075 --> 01:37:29.493
- Five degree up bubble.
- Mr Linkletter, man that periscope.

01:37:29.577 --> 01:37:31.244
Aye sir. Raising number two scope.

01:37:31.329 --> 01:37:34.498
Radio, Conn, Mr Vossler,

01:37:34.582 --> 01:37:37.834
this is Captain Kirk.
I need warp speed on that radio.

01:37:37.919 --> 01:37:39.211
Yes, sir.

01:37:40.755 --> 01:37:43.465
<i>Conn, Weapons, Russian missiles
will have launch capability</i>

01:37:43.549 --> 01:37:45.133
<i>in nine minutes.</i>

01:37:49.430 --> 01:37:50.764
- Oh, shit!
- What? What happened?

01:37:50.848 --> 01:37:52.265
Reattach that lead!

01:38:06.072 --> 01:38:08.240
Seventy-eight feet!
At periscope depth, sir!

01:38:08.282 --> 01:38:10.409
- Mr Linkletter!
- No close contact, sir.

01:38:10.451 --> 01:38:14.037
Very well. Chief of the watch,
raise the VLF radio antenna.

01:38:14.122 --> 01:38:16.081
Raise the VLF antenna. Aye, sir.

01:38:17.834 --> 01:38:19.668
VLF antenna coming up!

01:38:24.632 --> 01:38:27.759
Conn, Radio, sir, I think
she's breathing. We're getting close.

01:38:38.604 --> 01:38:40.313
- Halt, sir!
- Shoot me.

01:38:40.398 --> 01:38:42.482
- Shit. Shit.
- I got him.

01:38:44.318 --> 01:38:45.944
I have the conn.

01:38:48.448 --> 01:38:50.365
Give me my missile key.

01:38:59.083 --> 01:39:01.585
Give me the missile key, Mr Hunter.

01:39:15.558 --> 01:39:19.603
I'm the commander of this fucking ship!
Give me that goddamn key!

01:39:23.524 --> 01:39:26.860
<i>Conn, Weapons, Russian missiles
will have launch capability</i>

01:39:26.944 --> 01:39:28.612
<i>in seven minutes.</i>

01:39:29.989 --> 01:39:31.656
<i>Conn, Radio, sir!</i>

01:39:35.495 --> 01:39:36.536
Radio, Conn!

01:39:36.579 --> 01:39:40.040
Captain, Radio, Vossler, sir. She's
breathing again! We are really close!

01:39:41.000 --> 01:39:43.126
You got three minutes, Vossler.

01:39:43.211 --> 01:39:45.420
- Three minutes and counting!
- Yes, sir.

01:39:48.174 --> 01:39:49.716
You got three minutes.

01:40:00.061 --> 01:40:01.520
Come on.

01:40:19.997 --> 01:40:23.250
Come on, Vossler. Come on, come on.
Keep it going, keep it going.

01:40:30.466 --> 01:40:32.592
Speaking of horses,

01:40:33.928 --> 01:40:36.888
did you ever see
those Lipizzaner stallions?

01:40:37.431 --> 01:40:38.557
What?

01:40:39.684 --> 01:40:43.270
From Portugal.
The Lipizzaner stallions.

01:40:44.105 --> 01:40:47.649
The most highly trained horses
in the world. They're all white.

01:40:49.068 --> 01:40:50.360
Yes, sir.

01:40:52.029 --> 01:40:55.574
"Yes, sir" you're aware they're all white,

01:40:55.616 --> 01:40:57.576
or "yes, sir" you've seen them?

01:40:59.537 --> 01:41:01.538
Yes, sir, I've seen them.

01:41:01.956 --> 01:41:04.833
Yes, sir, I'm aware that they're all white.

01:41:05.710 --> 01:41:08.753
They're not from Portugal,
they're from Spain,

01:41:09.797 --> 01:41:12.757
and at birth, they're not white,
they're black.

01:41:14.677 --> 01:41:15.802
Sir.

01:41:16.804 --> 01:41:18.513
I didn't know that.

01:41:19.223 --> 01:41:21.308
But they are from Portugal.

01:41:25.313 --> 01:41:26.354
Come on, Vossler. Come on.

01:41:26.439 --> 01:41:30.817
- Yes. Yes.
- Come on. Come on. You got it.

01:41:33.863 --> 01:41:37.907
Some of the things they do dety belief.

01:41:39.285 --> 01:41:42.162
Their training programme
is simplicity itself.

01:41:42.997 --> 01:41:45.206
You just stick a cattle prod up their ass,

01:41:45.291 --> 01:41:47.876
and you can get a horse to deal cards.

01:41:48.919 --> 01:41:50.670
Simple matter of voltage.

01:41:59.430 --> 01:42:01.222
You're gonna get it. Come on.

01:42:03.809 --> 01:42:05.977
I almost had it. You saw it.

01:42:06.020 --> 01:42:08.021
Conn, Weapons,

01:42:08.648 --> 01:42:12.442
<i>Russian missiles will have
launch capability in four minutes.</i>

01:42:15.029 --> 01:42:17.864
- There you go! There you go!
- Ah, shit!

01:42:22.453 --> 01:42:25.955
Look, look, look! Look at it, Vossler!
There we go, there we go!

01:42:26.040 --> 01:42:27.040
Yes!

01:42:33.714 --> 01:42:36.758
Conn, Radio, we are receiving flash
traffic. Emergency action message.

01:42:36.842 --> 01:42:39.219
Recommend alert one.
Recommend alert one.

01:42:39.261 --> 01:42:40.679
Fuck, yeah!

01:42:41.806 --> 01:42:45.600
Alert one. Alert one.
Dougherty, Westergaurd, Zimmer.

01:42:45.935 --> 01:42:47.894
- Get that EAM.
- Aye-aye, sir.

01:42:51.273 --> 01:42:53.525
God help you if you're wrong.

01:42:54.318 --> 01:42:56.695
If I'm wrong, then we're at war.

01:42:57.863 --> 01:42:59.155
God help us all.

01:43:10.668 --> 01:43:14.421
Sir, we have a properly formatted
emergency action message

01:43:14.505 --> 01:43:16.256
from the National Command Authority,
sir.

01:43:16.298 --> 01:43:20.260
- Request permission to authenticate.
- Permission granted. Authenticate.

01:43:27.226 --> 01:43:31.771
"Delta, Delta, Sierra,
Bravo, Zulu, Delta, Tango."

01:43:36.569 --> 01:43:39.028
- Message is authentic, Captain.
- I concur, sir.

01:43:49.540 --> 01:43:51.040
I concur, sir.

01:43:51.625 --> 01:43:53.460
Message is authentic.

01:44:05.347 --> 01:44:06.473
1 MC.

01:44:08.517 --> 01:44:11.853
<i>Crew of the Alabama,
this is the captain.</i>

01:44:12.646 --> 01:44:14.522
Set condition 2SQ.

01:44:17.610 --> 01:44:19.569
Terminate launch, all missiles.

01:44:23.073 --> 01:44:24.908
All right! All right!

01:45:03.113 --> 01:45:05.114
Mr Hunter has the conn.

01:46:06.260 --> 01:46:09.053
<i>In the early hours of this morning,
Russian army forces moved in</i>

01:46:09.096 --> 01:46:11.764
<i>and met surprisingly little resistance.</i>

01:46:11.891 --> 01:46:13.766
<i>There were some sporadic battles</i>

01:46:13.851 --> 01:46:16.686
<i>but, apparently, the spectre
of fighting their countrymen</i>

01:46:16.770 --> 01:46:20.773
<i>proved too much for these rebel troops
